					<div class="rounded-2xl p-5 my-4 border border-gray-200" style="background-color: white;">
						<h4 class="font-bold mb-2" style="font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;">Drill 2: Fill in</h4>
						<p><span class="tibetan-text">ང་བོད་ཇ་འཐུང་</span> _____ (I want to drink Tibetan tea).</p>
